data.description: Stunning mid-century modern tucked away on a private wooded .40 acre lot! 3 bedrooms and 2 full renovated bathrooms. The oversized living room is great for hosting and entertaining with abundant natural light. Don't miss the renovated kitchen with ample cabinet space & counter space. Hardwoods throughout the home. Guest bedrooms make great home offices too. Both bathrooms are full renovated: new tiling, vanities and much more. The master suite is situated in the back of the home with great views of the private deck and backyard. It also includes a walk-in closet and private ensuite bathroom. Home includes a carport and storage closet. Close to restaurants and shops while being secluded in a dead end neighborhood!
